         <content>
            <TextArea fx:id="text" editable="false" prefHeight="352.0" prefWidth="540.0" text="Q: How do I get the information of a location?&#10;A: &#10;You can view the information of a location by simply hovering over it.&#10;&#10;Q: How do I find my path to a location?&#10;A: &#10;Step 1: Go to the home page, select the &quot;From&quot; box and click on the place you are at. &#10;Step 2: Select &quot;To&quot; box and click on where you want to go. &#10;Step 3: Hit on the green &quot;go&quot; button, the path will be highlighted in blue.&#10;(Tip: in case you pick the wrong location, click the red &quot;clear&quot; button. )&#10;(Tip: You can click and drag the starting location, the ending location, and any other location on the path.)&#10;&#10;Q: How do I find specific types of locations (example: bathrooms)?&#10;A: &#10;Step 1: Click on the dropdown 'Key Locations' in the upper left corner of the home page.&#10;Step 2: Select the type of location you desire (&quot;Bathrooms&quot;), and the locations on the current floor will be displayed on the map.&#10;(Tip: You can select one of the bathrooms as &quot;End Location&quot; and select your current location as &quot;Start Loction&quot;, then use the path finding feature to get your path to that restroom.)&#10;&#10;Q: How do I change floors of the map?&#10;A:&#10;Step 1: Click on the dropdown beside the label floor at the top and center of the home page.&#10;Step 2: Select which of the floors you want to see the map of.&#10;(Tip: Your starting and end locations can be on different floors!)&#10;&#10;Q: How do I change the building of the map?&#10;A:&#10;Step 1: Click on the dropdown beside the label building at the top and center of the home page.&#10;Step 2: Select which of the buildings you want to see the map of.&#10;(Tip: Your starting and end locations can be in different buildings!)&#10;&#10;Q: How do I send directions to myself?&#10;A:&#10;Step 1: Input your starting and end locations into the search boxes on the left side.&#10;Step 2: Hit 'Go.' This should display directions right under the 'Directions' tab.&#10;Step 3: Below the text directions, enter your email under the 'Send Directions' box.&#10;Step 4: Hit 'Send,' and you should receive directions in your mail within minutes.&#10;" wrapText="true" />
